Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.84,0:00:12.43,Main,,0,0,0,,My favorite food is... I guess, strawberries.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.43,0:00:15.22,Main,,0,0,0,,I see! You have cute tastes, Ms. Iona...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.22,0:00:19.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Look... Akira's popularity dropped again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.35,0:00:23.77,Main,,0,0,0,,She's seriously not good now...\NShe even ditches work too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.77,0:00:26.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, her style really doesn't match us anyways.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.44,0:00:28.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Like, she feels cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.49,0:00:32.32,Main,,0,0,0,,So what should we do about the\Nfront page model for the next mag?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.32,0:00:36.04,Main,,0,0,0,,You want to drop Akira and go with Yuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.04,0:00:40.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, that's nice... It would be great\Nif they took that talk somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.29,0:00:44.46,Main,,0,0,0,,I like having them with sugar and milk.\NNot with condensed milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.46,0:00:46.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh...? Oh, right, strawberries.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.96,0:00:48.84,Main,,0,0,0,,I use the back of my fork...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.84,0:00:51.05,Main,,0,0,0,,...to smash them to bits.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.35,0:00:59.64,Main,,0,0,0,,If I win... I'll make you apologize to Hitoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.94,0:01:01.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.66,0:01:21.71,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The truth rests solely on{\i0}\N{\i1}the front/back of a card{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.71,0:01:27.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It has not yet been solved{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.00,0:01:37.01,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Upon the dazzling, dizzying stage,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.01,0:01:48.36,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}destroy those entangled emotions{\i0}\N{\i1}as many times as it takes to satisfy you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.36,0:01:53.57,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What should the tomorrows{\i0}\N{\i1}wandering after fate's beckoning{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.57,0:01:58.95,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}choose and discard so that{\i0}\N{\i1}they can become one?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.95,0:02:04.42,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't afford to disclose my reproachable hand{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.42,0:02:09.50,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The days spent draining{\i0}\N{\i1}the already-dry sea of regret{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.50,0:02:14.93,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}desire within limited words forgiveness{\i0}\N{\i1}for the unplanned smile{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.93,0:02:19.81,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't mind forgetting reality{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.81,0:02:24.94,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't want to know anything now{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.94,0:02:26.19,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.69,0:02:35.16,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm home...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.45,0:02:40.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe! What happened? You're all wet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.04,0:02:45.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Where are your friends?\NWeren't you with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.88,0:02:51.13,Main,,0,0,0,,You better wipe yourself off,\Nor else you'll catch a cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.38,0:02:53.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.72,0:03:03.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm first! Aki-lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.85,0:03:05.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Piruluk-{\i1}tan{\i0}, show your stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.81,0:03:09.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't go easy on her just\Nbecause she's a scrub, you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.86,0:03:11.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Say, Ru?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.32,0:03:12.36,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.36,0:03:15.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama can battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.24,0:03:18.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.99,0:03:23.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Draw. I'll drop a card in the\NEner Zone. Piruluk-{\i1}tan{\i0}, Grow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.41,0:03:26.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, and I'll summon Sky Cat-{\i1}chan {\i0}too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.54,0:03:30.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama, Grow! I summon Kukri and Ponya!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.09,0:03:34.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't get too excited, squirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.97,0:03:38.55,Main,,0,0,0,,What... is this feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.55,0:03:41.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Battling Akira is going to be painful...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.55,0:03:43.72,Main,,0,0,0,,It is painful...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.64,0:03:46.60,Main,,0,0,0,,...but!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.60,0:03:51.36,Main,,0,0,0,,The hell?! I thought she\Nwas a WIXOSS newbie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.36,0:03:53.02,Main,,0,0,0,,She is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.02,0:03:56.07,Main,,0,0,0,,It seems as if this is her first serious battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.07,0:03:57.24,Main,,0,0,0,,What...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.24,0:03:58.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Gifted...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.53,0:04:01.12,Main,,0,0,0,,She is quite gifted.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.12,0:04:05.54,Main,,0,0,0,,What? You trying to tell me\Nsomething? That I'm not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.79,0:04:10.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Piruluk! You're pissing me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.00,0:04:12.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Just shut your mouth and follow my commands!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.84,0:04:15.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm just gonna get this over quick...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.05,0:04:16.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Arts!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.09,0:04:18.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Peeping Analyze.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.34,0:04:20.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru-ru?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.88,0:04:24.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Looks like you're following\Ntextbook examples there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.68,0:04:29.60,Main,,0,0,0,,So, that means... you must have a lot of...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.69,0:04:32.23,Main,,0,0,0,,...level 4s!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.32,0:04:36.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Missed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.94,0:04:40.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Damn it...! Who cares if I missed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.78,0:04:44.95,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to know what her wish is, Piruluk!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:46.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.66,0:04:52.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru-ru? I wonder if you'll be all\Nouchy-ouchy if I see your wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.50,0:04:57.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Come on, Piruluk-{\i1}tan{\i0}!\NGo ahead and show me her pains!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.67,0:04:58.71,Main,,0,0,0,,I see nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.71,0:04:59.84,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.84,0:05:04.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop acting like\Nsome broken piece of trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.18,0:05:05.93,Main,,0,0,0,,She has...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.93,0:05:07.39,Main,,0,0,0,,...no wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.35,0:05:15.02,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right... I... have no wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.02,0:05:21.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?! A-Are you serious?! You're\Nbattling as a Selector without any wishes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.78,0:05:26.33,Main,,0,0,0,,No way! You've got to be kidding?!\NThat makes no sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.33,0:05:30.33,Main,,0,0,0,,All the Selectors are, like,\Nsuper serious and stuff, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.33,0:05:35.17,Main,,0,0,0,,You've been battling for\Nthe fun of it?! You're so horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.17,0:05:39.80,Main,,0,0,0,,A person without a wish participating\Nin WIXOSS as a Selector...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.80,0:05:41.34,Main,,0,0,0,,...is blasphemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.34,0:05:43.18,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't care what you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.18,0:05:44.68,Main,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.68,0:05:49.35,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't have any wishes,\Nso I'm not scared of anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.35,0:05:50.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Arc Aura!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.73,0:05:52.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.91,0:06:09.66,Main,,0,0,0,,What the hell is wrong with you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.66,0:06:12.79,Main,,0,0,0,,You don't have any wishes... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.79,0:06:14.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.37,0:06:18.34,Main,,0,0,0,,...why the hell are you trying to stop mine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.34,0:06:21.51,Main,,0,0,0,,I-I just wanted you to...\Napologize to Hitoe, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.51,0:06:24.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop frekkin' lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.01,0:06:29.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Beating me until I groveled...\NYou were enjoying it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.93,0:06:31.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.25,0:06:54.83,Main,,0,0,0,,"With Ruko and Yuzuki..."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.83,0:06:57.13,Main,,0,0,0,,"...playing WIXOSS at the library."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.13,0:07:00.67,Main,,0,0,0,,"On our way back,\Nwe bought stuffed dumplings..."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.67,0:07:02.59,Main,,0,0,0,,"Ru... ko..."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.59,0:07:03.96,Main,,0,0,0,,"Yuzu..."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.98,0:07:19.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.90,0:07:22.48,Main,,0,0,0,,What's the matter Hitoe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.48,0:07:24.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Words... disappearing...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.53,0:07:25.36,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.36,0:07:29.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Disappearing! All the words in my notebook...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.91,0:07:31.99,Main,,0,0,0,,...are disappearing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.99,0:07:34.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Disappearing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.75,0:07:36.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.50,0:07:39.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Is Akira late again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.88,0:07:42.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona? Do you know where Akira is?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.71,0:07:44.05,Main,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.05,0:07:47.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Screw it... That brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.22,0:07:50.26,Main,,0,0,0,,It's set. Akira's off for next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.26,0:07:52.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Better yet, why won't we\Njust drop her for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.85,0:07:54.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.52,0:08:01.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.28,0:08:10.20,Main,,0,0,0,,I sense battle... And a losing one at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.12,0:08:16.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you remember that\Npoor girl that battled Iona?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.00,0:08:22.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Looks like that was her\Nsecond battle, and her second defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.09,0:08:27.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Lose one more, and she loses her wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.88,0:08:31.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Then you approached\Nthat poor, cornered girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.43,0:08:37.68,Main,,0,0,0,,You sweet-talked her into battle\Nwith a free win as bait...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.68,0:08:42.15,Main,,0,0,0,,You're the one who ended that poor girl\Nwho just lost her second battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.15,0:08:47.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Her wish... Her life...\NYou reaped them away from her...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.36,0:08:52.62,Main,,0,0,0,,You got a problem with that?!\NIt's my choice how I battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.62,0:08:54.95,Main,,0,0,0,,You're right. It is your choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.95,0:08:57.54,Main,,0,0,0,,But, too bad about the next battle after...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.54,0:09:00.83,Main,,0,0,0,,You lost so easily to that girl Iona beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.00,0:09:06.25,Main,,0,0,0,,That's why you stopped feeding off\Nthe scraps that Iona left behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.25,0:09:09.63,Main,,0,0,0,,...and started looking\Nfor weaker, new Selectors.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.42,0:09:13.01,Main,,0,0,0,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.01,0:09:15.05,Main,,0,0,0,,You lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.05,0:09:16.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.35,0:09:21.44,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't want your perverted hands\Nto disgrace Selector battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.44,0:09:22.52,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.52,0:09:26.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Your wish is... to see Iona's life ruined...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.73,0:09:29.53,Main,,0,0,0,,You want to beat Iona, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.53,0:09:33.49,Main,,0,0,0,,But if so, isn't it weird for you\Nto avoid battling Iona?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.49,0:09:36.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Like I said, it's my choice how I battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.95,0:09:40.08,Main,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter because if I win,\Nyou're going to bite the dust!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.08,0:09:41.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.17,0:09:46.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Looks like Yuko's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.34,0:09:49.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute... I thought the\Nshoot today was with me and Iona...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.96,0:09:53.18,Main,,0,0,0,,You don't have a shoot today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.18,0:09:54.18,Main,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.18,0:09:57.85,Main,,0,0,0,,While you were so busy\Nlooking for Selectors...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.85,0:10:01.23,Main,,0,0,0,,...you've lost your place here, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.39,0:10:09.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, you poor thing! How ironic to see you\N"bite the dust" before Iona does... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.44,0:10:13.78,Main,,0,0,0,,I need to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.91,0:10:17.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.41,0:10:23.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Who cares if my life is ruined...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.96,0:10:28.88,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna tear your life\Nto shreds with my own hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.67,0:10:32.67,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess its game over for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.10,0:10:41.10,Main,,0,0,0,,It doesn't look like you have a fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.10,0:10:43.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you still feel sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.18,0:10:46.65,Main,,0,0,0,,My head hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.65,0:10:52.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, let me call school and\Nlet them know you'll be off today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.45,0:10:59.91,Main,,0,0,0,,I made Grandma worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.91,0:11:01.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.66,0:11:04.71,Main,,0,0,0,,You were enjoying it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.75,0:11:11.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Why am I enjoying battles so much...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.38,0:11:17.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Even when I know what horrible things will\Nhappen if I continue to battle... And still...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.09,0:11:19.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't cry, Ru.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.76,0:11:24.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama likes seeing Ru having fun battling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.23,0:11:27.02,Main,,0,0,0,,So, don't cry. We can have plenty of battles...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.02,0:11:28.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.94,0:11:30.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.98,0:11:35.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kazuki? Let's go out sometime!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.57,0:11:37.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.15,0:11:38.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Sure, why not? Let's head out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.82,0:11:40.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoa! That's unusual of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.45,0:11:42.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Say, let's get something to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.66,0:11:43.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.62,0:11:45.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.62,0:11:47.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Can I speak with you for a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.59,0:11:54.92,Main,,0,0,0,,You know? You and Kazuki\Naren't leaving a good impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.92,0:11:55.63,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.63,0:11:59.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Like, everyone's creeped out\Nseeing you both together all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.18,0:12:01.01,Main,,0,0,0,,That was blunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.01,0:12:05.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't make that face.\NWe're really worried about you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.60,0:12:06.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.48,0:12:10.90,Main,,0,0,0,,It felt bad hearing all the bad rumors about\Nyou two, so I wanted to give you some advice...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.90,0:12:12.61,Main,,0,0,0,,What's that to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.61,0:12:14.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Why would you care?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.53,0:12:21.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, to be exact, I'm only concerned\Nabout Kazuki-{\i1}kun{\i0}. You? I couldn't care less.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.83,0:12:26.25,Main,,0,0,0,,I mean, I felt bad seeing\NKazuki-{\i1}kun {\i0}stalked by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.25,0:12:30.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. You may not know,\Nbut Kazuki-{\i1}kun {\i0}is pretty popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.92,0:12:33.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Just because you're around,\Nall the bad rumors...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.80,0:12:35.88,Main,,0,0,0,,What an attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.88,0:12:38.38,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess that means that rumor is real...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.38,0:12:39.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.26,0:12:46.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.27,0:12:47.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.31,0:12:48.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't talk to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.94,0:12:54.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Everyone... What's wrong with everyone...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.61,0:12:57.40,Main,,0,0,0,,They're the creeps...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.40,0:12:59.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Hi ya there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.16,0:13:04.70,Main,,0,0,0,,You're a Selector, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:09.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Yay! I finally met one! Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.25,0:13:14.54,Main,,0,0,0,,It's so hard finding Selectors, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.54,0:13:18.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Can you please, oh pretty please,\Nbattle with cute, little Chiyori?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.42,0:13:20.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Let me... advise you something...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.92,0:13:22.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.76,0:13:25.47,Main,,0,0,0,,In Selector battles...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.47,0:13:28.43,Main,,0,0,0,,...if you lose, you're going\Nto be in a lot of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.43,0:13:29.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.48,0:13:31.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Yessy! I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.06,0:13:35.07,Main,,0,0,0,,It's written right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.15,0:13:38.78,Main,,0,0,0,,A WIXOSS... novel...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.78,0:13:39.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:43.53,Main,,0,0,0,,If you lose three times, the WIXOSS\Nfactors expand inside your body...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.53,0:13:48.24,Main,,0,0,0,,...like a hot air balloon,\Nand you "{\i1}Kaboom{\i0}!" and die, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.24,0:13:50.08,Main,,0,0,0,,That's so scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.91,0:13:51.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait, that's not--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.87,0:13:58.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Battling regardless of that, for the sake\Nof fulfilling your wish, is so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.34,0:14:00.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.97,0:14:04.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry there. My girl here is a bit soft\Non the top, if you know what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.89,0:14:09.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow that's so rude, Eldora!\NAt least I'm strong in battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.39,0:14:18.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Anyways! My precious Selector-{\i1}san{\i0}. I'd like\Nto offer my commemorative first battle to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.32,0:14:20.28,Main,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.28,0:14:24.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh come on, Kazuki-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.70,0:14:26.87,Main,,0,0,0,,That's not true...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.87,0:14:28.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's go some place!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.16,0:14:29.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, uh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.91,0:14:33.08,Main,,0,0,0,,There's so many things I want to ask you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.04,0:14:38.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's do this! Please?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.75,0:14:39.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.75,0:14:41.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.26,0:14:43.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.80,0:14:48.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Yay! Yay! It's time to battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.68,0:14:57.61,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be stepping out for a bit,\Nso have a good rest, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.82,0:15:09.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Why do I feel like... I've been\Nlooking for something all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.66,0:15:14.71,Main,,0,0,0,,If I can't have that something...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.71,0:15:19.09,Main,,0,0,0,,I feel like there is no reason to be alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.97,0:15:30.47,Main,,0,0,0,,I lost... I lost, I tell you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.47,0:15:34.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she's strong.\NWay stronger than you, Chiyori.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.60,0:15:37.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Like, so sorry to have bothered you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.27,0:15:43.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Come on, Eldora! All great\Nheroines lose their first battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.11,0:15:46.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah right. Like, only in novels.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.11,0:15:48.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh! Let me give you this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.57,0:15:50.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's get together again, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.66,0:15:52.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.54,0:16:00.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.09,0:16:02.38,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess I won.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.38,0:16:04.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.05,0:16:08.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Losing three times means\Nmy wish won't come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.30,0:16:14.18,Main,,0,0,0,,But there's no telling how many times I would\Nneed to win for my wish to come true, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.18,0:16:16.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Only when the conditions are met...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.43,0:16:21.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Conditions? That's a weird way to word it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.23,0:16:24.36,Main,,0,0,0,,I feel like you'll tell me\Nsomething again later...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.36,0:16:29.61,Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder what would happen\Nif my wish is reversed?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.61,0:16:31.03,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.03,0:16:34.41,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll never be with Kazuki again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.41,0:16:36.75,Main,,0,0,0,,No, it has to be worse than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.75,0:16:40.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe Kazuki will hate me and\NI'll never be able to see him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.55,0:16:47.51,Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder where Kazuki went?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.51,0:16:48.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.80,0:16:51.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe he went to Momoka-{\i1}san{\i0}'s\Nplace to choose cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.85,0:16:54.72,Main,,0,0,0,,The others with him seemed new to the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.72,0:16:56.98,Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder if he's showing\Nthem all sorts of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.98,0:16:58.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki, listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.27,0:17:02.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Or maybe they went to the movies\Nand stopped by the food court
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.23,0:17:03.94,Main,,0,0,0,,to play some games.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.94,0:17:09.90,Main,,0,0,0,,They may go out for some {\i1}Okonomiyaki{\i0}, and\Nthen they'll exchange their addresses, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.90,0:17:11.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.57,0:17:13.87,Main,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.45,0:17:20.08,Main,,0,0,0,,If Kazuki is going to be taken away\Nfrom me, I'd rather disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.42,0:17:27.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if you're upset,\Nyou should never say such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.42,0:17:29.42,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm serious...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.42,0:17:31.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Hanayo-{\i1}san{\i0}, you're a liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.59,0:17:38.60,Main,,0,0,0,,But... I need you to have\Na chance for my wish to come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.60,0:17:43.10,Main,,0,0,0,,I lost to Akira. But I was\Nable to beat that girl, Chiyori.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.10,0:17:48.07,Main,,0,0,0,,If I still have the chance to win...\NIf the chance to get Kazuki isn't gone yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.07,0:17:50.40,Main,,0,0,0,,If my wish isn't gone yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.40,0:17:54.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Rather than having him taken from me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.12,0:17:55.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.20,0:18:02.66,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm your LRIG... I'll follow you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.66,0:18:04.17,Main,,0,0,0,,...no matter where.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.75,0:18:14.68,Main,,0,0,0,,When I was living with Mom,\NI don't think I asked for much...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.68,0:18:19.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Mom seemed so busy being by herself...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.35,0:18:20.64,Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.64,0:18:23.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know what Ruko is thinking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.89,0:18:25.73,Main,,0,0,0,,She scares me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.73,0:18:31.03,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't know why I was scaring\Nmy mom... and that scared me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.78,0:18:32.44,Main,,0,0,0,,"Kominato"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.44,0:18:34.36,Main,,0,0,0,,"Kominato"\NI'm fine as long as I have
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.36,0:18:35.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Grandma and my brother with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.91,0:18:44.29,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to make anyone scared again,\Nso I didn't ask for much, I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.29,0:18:45.88,Main,,0,0,0,,And still...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.63,0:18:53.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama likes seeing Ru having fun battling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.59,0:18:59.89,Main,,0,0,0,,No... No, no...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.27,0:19:06.98,Main,,0,0,0,,The hell you acting like you've been a victim?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.98,0:19:13.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Beating me until I groveled...\NYou were enjoying it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.36,0:19:18.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru-{\i1}chan{\i0}... Ru-{\i1}chan{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.70,0:19:21.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Wake up, Ru-{\i1}chan{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.04,0:19:24.96,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I said you were asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.96,0:19:26.42,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.85,0:19:46.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to bother you all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.89,0:19:51.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you like parfaits? I just\Nordered it, but I hope you like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.82,0:19:53.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.07,0:19:57.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe loved eating {\i1}marron{\i0}\Nparfaits. This one looks good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.40,0:20:00.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should bring her here next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.28,0:20:02.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.62,0:20:09.29,Main,,0,0,0,,I found your number and\NYuzuki-{\i1}san{\i0}'s number in Hitoe's cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.42,0:20:14.80,Main,,0,0,0,,You must think I'm a horrible mother\Nlooking at her daughter's phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.80,0:20:15.92,Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.92,0:20:18.84,Main,,0,0,0,,That's... the memo Hitoe\Nwas keeping on battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.84,0:20:20.10,Main,,0,0,0,,You know this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.10,0:20:21.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.55,0:20:26.93,Main,,0,0,0,,The words written here...\NHitoe told me that she can't see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.93,0:20:29.44,Main,,0,0,0,,She also said she doesn't know you girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.69,0:20:39.28,Main,,0,0,0,,"Today, I bought a matching pair\Nof scrunchies with Ruko and Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.28,0:20:46.37,Main,,0,0,0,,They were both really cute with them.\NThey said I was cute too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.37,0:20:51.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Exchanging all the fun and happy words\Nwith everyone... made me happier
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.42,0:20:54.59,Main,,0,0,0,,than how I already was.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.59,0:20:57.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Friends are really beautiful."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.51,0:21:04.60,Main,,0,0,0,,She was very happy about making friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.60,0:21:07.14,Main,,0,0,0,,But, now she's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.14,0:21:11.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko-{\i1}san{\i0}? If there's anything you know or\Nmay have noticed, can you please tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.31,0:21:13.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if you had an argument with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.65,0:21:17.40,Main,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not trying to place blame or anything,\Nbut it looks like something went off in her,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.40,0:21:19.07,Main,,0,0,0,,and she's all in shock, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.03,0:21:25.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.41,0:21:29.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe lost three times...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.50,0:21:35.59,Main,,0,0,0,,We didn't know what would happen if we lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.59,0:21:41.43,Main,,0,0,0,,It was fun... battling together\Njust for fun... And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.43,0:21:45.22,Main,,0,0,0,,R-Ruko-{\i1}san{\i0}? Calm down there...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.01,0:21:47.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko-{\i1}san{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.02,0:21:52.77,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.98,0:21:55.61,Main,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.61,0:21:58.32,Main,,0,0,0,,...don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.49,0:22:01.36,Main,,0,0,0,,...what to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.24,0:22:14.04,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nodding to the clockwork shadow{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.04,0:22:19.84,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}opens the door to the end,{\i0}\N{\i1}bringing in the darkness{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.84,0:22:25.64,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There we catch glimpses of the perilous answer{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.64,0:22:31.56,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Today's prayer becomes taboo tomorrow{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.56,0:22:37.23,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The upside-down maze reflects{\i0}\N{\i1}the heavens and the earth{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.23,0:22:43.15,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The gear begins to turn{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.15,0:22:49.33,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Listen carefully among the masses{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.33,0:22:59.25,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and that bell resounding in{\i0}\N{\i1}the skies beckons the soul...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.59,0:23:06.68,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must move forward even beyond eternity{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.68,0:23:12.27,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because it is the future I chose{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.27,0:23:18.36,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The unreachable summer clouds{\i0}\N{\i1}and flickering heat haze{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.36,0:23:25.11,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One day I'll get back my place of smiles{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.87,0:23:35.79,Main,,0,0,0,,So you wanted to do it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.79,0:23:37.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Why are you saying this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.96,0:23:39.96,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to do it with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.96,0:23:40.96,Main,,0,0,0,,...I want to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.96,0:23:44.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Just give up, and have some fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.42,0:23:47.01,Main,,0,0,0,,"The Girl's Desire."
